# TypeScript

- Shared types/interfaces: **`src/lib/Type/`** 폴더에서 타입별 파일로 관리. `Type/index.ts`에서 re-export. 사용처: `import type { ... } from '$lib/Type'`. (기존 호환용 `board-types.ts`는 Type+Enum re-export)
- Use `interface` for object shapes, `type` for unions and aliases
- Avoid `any`; prefer `unknown` + narrowing / type guards
- Derived / computed values → `$derived`, not a raw `const` inside `$effect`
